The Vital Point for Death (43)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par Given that three white stones are being captured, it looks hopeless for white to drive black towards death.
\par
\par However, when you consider the possibility of black having a shortage of liberties, you can solve this problem easier than you think.
\par }
