Diagram 3 (The Vital Point)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If white crawls in at 1 to reduce black's eyespace, it induces black 2 and white fails. Black 2 is the vital point for black and white.
\par
\par Now even if white plays at \b\f1 A\b0\f0 , it is only a pik in husu.
\par }
